
This is explodomatica.

It is an attempt to automate the process shown in this
video: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u3KHg2AwpMM

See http://smcameron.github.com/explodomatica

Note: this program depends on the following libraries:

libvorbis   http://xiph.org/   Your distro probably already has this.
portaudio   http://www.portaudio.com/  You need v19, not v18. 
sndfile     http://www.mega-nerd.com/libsndfile/  Your distro may have this already.



